                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-2">
                      [2]. Voir la <bibl><ptr target="PBW"/>, <citedRange unit="entry"><ref target="http://pbw2016.kdl.kcl.ac.uk/person/Kyriakos/101/">Kyriakos 101</ref></citedRange></bibl>.
                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-3">
                      [3]. <bibl><ptr target="ScylitzaeSynopsis1973"/>, <citedRange unit="page">p. 375, l. 58-60</citedRange></bibl>; 
                      <bibl><ptr target="SkylitzèsEmpereurs2003"/>, <citedRange>p. 311 et n. 4</citedRange></bibl>; 
                      <bibl><ptr target="Cedrenus1839"/>, <citedRange unit="page">p. 486, l. 11-13</citedRange></bibl>. Sur le
                      titre de syncelle, voir aussi <bibl><ptr target="LaurentCorpus5.1"/>, <citedRange unit="page">p. 147-148</citedRange></bibl>.
                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-4">
                      [4]. <bibl><ptr target="Ficker1911"/>, <citedRange unit="page">p. 18, l. 30</citedRange> (année 1030), <citedRange unit="page">42, l. 8</citedRange> (année 1039)</bibl>. 
